Please get the following sources 
SDL-1.2.14.tar.xz 
SDL_image-1.2.10.tar.xz
SDL_mixer-1.2.11.tar.xz
SDL_net-1.2.7.tar.xz 
SDL_ttf-2.0.10.tar.xz 

from
http://slackware.osuosl.org/slackware-current/source/l/sdl/
or
http://slackware.osuosl.org/slackware64-current/source/l/sdl/

and place it onto this directory and you can start rebuilding SDL with an additional patch
